Snappy,is,a,collaborative,customer,service,system,Its,email,ticket,support,system,can,be,used,from,any,email,client,and,includes,a,tagging,service,that,makes,it,easier,to,assign,and,respond,to,support,tickets,Snappy,also,allows,users,to,create,organized,single,page,FAQs,to,help,customers,find,the,information,they,need,Staff,can,access,FAQ,answers,and,easily,include,them,in,support,emails,The,Team,Wall,provides,a,place,where,customer,support,personnel,can,chat,and,exchange,information,Snappy,s,reporting,system,provides,information,on,metrics,like,how,many,tickets,are,being,processed,how,long,each,ticket,takes,to,handle,and,what,issues,are,arising,most,frequently,Snappy,can,be,accessed,programmatically,for,integration,with,other,systems,and,services,using,REST,calls